<img src="/content/dam/news-events/news/2019/09/candice-monson-2.jpg" alt="Candice Monson sits at the head of a conference table teaching a class of students sitting around the table"/>




					 
						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p>Monson’s work includes evaluating the best methods to train clinicians in the treatments she has developed. Photo by Sarah Palmer.</p>
</div>
						    
					
				</div>
